snippet.title: Elsinore - Launch Trailer (July 22)
snippet.description:
ELSINORE is a time-looping tragedy where you alter the story by changing what characters know. Time marches relentlessly on towards a bloody end. Can you sway your friends and family from their paths?

ELSINORE launches via Steam on PC, Mac and Linux on July 22.

Website: https://elsinore-game.com/
Store Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/512890/Elsinore/
